channel.title: RuneDesign [Approved]
channel.description:
[size=18pt]Originally posted on Rune-Server.[/size]
If you have a run.bat error look at this
Why? I just dont feel like coding 614s anymore. Seriously, that's all I can. Ive been working really hard on this, and im proud to release. This has no anti leechs, no MySQL, nothing. I do not want this to be released on anywhere else then google! Im gonna start again with a 317 server, and learn java coding after school. I wish everyone good luck with this, and I hope you enjoy this. Please use the thanks button, and leave a comment. Feel free to rep or anything else. If I see this anywhere else then R-S, then I will delete all links, and flame ya 24/7. I only want to have it uploaded on my dropbox.
If you need any help, or if you have errors etc please feel free to report them. I don't care about leechers. Feel free to leech anything you want, but please give some Credits and show some respect.
Some features: - Workign Teleblock with timer - Working Trading without item duplication - Working Dicing - Working Potion system/eating system - Perfect combat (No overpowered items) - 100% Antiflood - 50% Working friendlist - NO NULLPOINTERS! Stable source - Working bonuses - Super Donator/Premium Donator/Legit Dicer - Working leeches - No dupes - 6 Different PK spots - 3 Multi zones - Usefull commands - Blood/Miasmic barrage - Working Ring of Vigour - Working divine affects

Client Link: http://uppit.com/4d8ytd5kbz46/Working_614_Client.rar
Cache Link: YOU DONT NEED TO DOWNLOAD THIS JUST LOOK AT MY RUN.BAT TUT (place it in your c:/ and you wont get run errors!) : http://dl.dropbox.com/u/48084005/cache.zip To change your client ip change the ip in client.java, applet_sub1.java and launch.java
